ziegfeld girl is a 1941 metro-goldwyn-mayer musical film starring james stewart , judy garland , hedy lamarr , lana turner , tony martin , jackie cooper , eve arden , and philip dorn .   the film was directed by robert z. leonard and featured musical numbers by busby berkeley .   set in the 1920s , the film tells the parallel stories of three women who become performers in the renowned broadway show the ziegfeld follies .   it was intended to be a 1938 sequel to the 1936 hit the great ziegfeld , and recycled some footage from the earlier film .